3 Minute Games, Inc
Privacy Policy for Games Distributed on Apple Arcade
Last updated: Jan 01, 2023
Our games do not collect, process or store any personal data. We may collect non-personal data using the Apple Gamecenter service to support features like Achievements and Leaderboards. Such data is stored by Apple and is subject to the privacy policy for that service. To stop sending data to Gamecenter you must sign out of Gamecenter in Apple Settings. We do not collect, process, or store any non-personal data on our servers.
Our games handle the data of underage users in the same way as all other users. Any data collected from underage users is used exclusively to support the internal operation of our games.
We do not send data to any third-party partners.
If you have any questions please contact us at support@3minute.games.